** \\[Rho] ** Dagger[aj] cj, {j, ...}]. Supermap[{a1, a2, ...}, {{c 11, c 12, \
...}, {c 21, c 22, ...}, ...}] represents mapping \\[Rho] \\[RightTeeArrow] \
Sum[ai ** \\[Rho] ** Dagger[aj] cij, {i, ...}, {j, ...}]. Supermap[tsr] \
represents the supermap corresponding to Choi matrix tsr. Supermap[...][rho] \
maps rho according to the operator-sum representation.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "Supermap", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
    "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> "Supermap", "type" -> "Symbol", 
